author: Benedict Correya
text: One of the nicest Anytime Fitness gyms I‚Äôve visited! The gym is spacious, clean, and well-equipped with a wide range of machines and weights. The location inside City Square Mall is very convenient. Staff are friendly, and the overall atmosphere is motivating ‚Äî great place for a solid workout.

author: Michael Thein
text:

author: Justin Hoyo
text:
One of the better anytime fitness outlets in Singapore‚Äôs by far. The gym is extremely spacious, well-equipped, and well maintained. It‚Äôs location within city square mall which is convenient from MRT. There‚Äôs a total of six power racks and two smith machines. Cable stations are also available. They also have dedicated changing room/toilet area.

Would be willing to travel here on the weekends. I would assume weekday evenings will be packed. Come and check this gym out! ‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è

author: khrhms
text: Stumbled upon this awesome AF outlet while at the area for lunch. Great facilities, huge and super clean. So many equipments to choose from! The showers are clean and the female toilets even have sanitary pads. Bath soap and shampoo also provided. Will come again to work out here more often.

author: Jane Jha
text:
‚Ä¢ Gym's sanitizer spray are often empty, making it difficult to maintain hygiene.

‚Ä¢ The wiping cloth provided are consistently dirty, dusty, and have a strong odor. Wet wipes dispenser are always empty

‚Ä¢ Members are forced to bring their own wipes because hygiene is essential, yet the gym doesn't supply these basic necessities.

‚Ä¢ Despite a rule requiring members to sanitize equipment after use, basic cleaning supplies are not provided.

‚Ä¢ Despite paying monthly fees, we are expected to supply our own cleaning materials, and the equipment is frequently dusty and poorly mentained

I am sharing my experience here because submitting feedback through the QR code provided doesn‚Äôt seem to reach management. Nothing has changed, and only getting worse.

author: Zero!
text: Really love this gym! The place is clean, spacious, and has all the equipment I need. Everything is well-maintained and even when it gets a bit busy, I never have trouble finding a machine. The staff are super friendly and always willing to help out, which makes the atmosphere really welcoming. Plus, the location inside City Square Mall is super convenient for me. Definitely recommend this branch of Anytime Fitness!

author: Rachel Citrella
text: This gym is big and spacious. They have more machines than the average AF. For example, they have 2 smith machines and I don‚Äôt have to wait. Environment is nice with their friendly staff. I don‚Äôt usually frequent here but I might just drop by whenever I‚Äôm in town.

author: CALLISTA SHANNON
text: Kyan Joseph Dian are amazing staff with impeccable customer service . I requested for the genre of songs and they acceded to my request without any complaints. The gym is clean and nicely maintained and smells amazing. 10/10 recommend , it‚Äôs one of my favourite outlets. ! It also has amazing sunlight if you like to take gym videos

author: Alexander Aaltonen
text:
Visited this AF outlet a few times as I was staying nearby. All in all a very decent gym with a good variety of machines and equipment -- perfect for any kind of exercise!

Gets a bit crowdy after work, but still manageable! The outlet is tucked away all the way up to the 6th level of the mall, might be a bit tricky to find if you're visiting the first time.

author: Michael Bruh
text:
Very good gym. Clean and friendly environment.

I had pleasant experience with the receptionist, Daryl. He was very friendly and informative

author: Termy Gator
text:
Excellent gym with top of the line equipment and excellent amenities, clean toilet in a nutshell. Can be a tad bit crowded but excellent service rendered by the staff more than superseded the dense gym population.

Special mention to Daryl who took the time to run me through some of the equipment despite me being rather lost and intimidated by all the muscly men and women there. He was patient and knowledgeable and I honestly thought he was a PT. Turns out he was just a regular staff there, regular staff also so knowledgeable omg, their PT must be insane.

author: jourdan wee
text:
The gym itself is very updated and filled with great machines, and the staff members are polite and nice.

However I would caution females to come here. The males in this outlet would use the females only toilets & bathrooms, despite blatant posters on the door indicating the female‚Äôs side. I would not recommend any females to come in here for their privacy and safety. If you have to, you are better off using the shopping mall‚Äôs toilet in the same level.

author: zeny lim
text: Well equipped gym with fully functional machines. Clean and friendly staff.

author: Bryan
text:
Really well equipped and spacious gym.

Staff are very friendly

Many power racks to do deadlifts bench or squat. All with high quality LF equipment .

Hope that the gym will add more chairs to sit in after gymming to enjoy our protein shakes

author: Ashish Bokil
text:
I recently visited Anytime Fitness at City Square Mall with my two boys, and we all had a fantastic experience. The gym has a really positive and motivating atmosphere, which is exactly what we need to get our workouts oingg). Everyone there, from staff to other gym-goers, seemed friendly and focused on their fitness goals.

The gym itself is spacious and well-equipped, with plenty of machines and weights to accommodate different workout styles. My boys especially enjoyed the variety of cardio options. We'll definitely be back for another family workout soon!

Easy option to shop n workout n eat

author: Winfred Tham
text: Went to this AF the environment was very welcoming and good, had a good variety of machines as well. Staff were very kind and welcoming as well. And very quick and efficient to answer my questions or requests. Overall I would say of all the AF i have been at this would be the best AF I worked out at. Would recommend other to come here.

author: Aye Chan
text: Spacious. Great view. Good variety of quality equipments. Members have awesome gym etiquette. Cleanliness is exceptional. Generous amount of disinfectant spray bottles throughout the gym. Staffs are cheerful and approachable. Always a good experience coming here.

author: Kiat Long Tay
text: Of the many AF outlets I've been to, this one is 5 stars. First, with 6 powerlifting racks, 2 Smith machines, and 3 dual-cable machines, I don't ever have to worry about being too crowded and having to queue for machines. Second, it's clean! And tidy - all handles, clips, spray bottles etc are all placed in small baskets around the gym. There's enough racks for each weight plate, so I don't have to "play the Tower of Hanoi" every time. Third, with two pairs of every dumbbell in 2.5kg increments, and a separate rack just for 25kg red plates, surely got enough weights for everyone.

author: Ortho Bog
text:
Gym Staff - 0 stars (very bad attitude and rude) - had several issues during last one year and they always are very arrogant and rude. They are also not clear on the policies and always keep changing based on their mood.

Equipment and gym - 4/5
Cleanliness - 1/5

I just go during early morning so that dont have to see the lazy and useless staff. Hope management can hire someone with some professional attitude who can actually help instead of just sitting and the only answer the staff have for all problem is ‚Äúwhat can i do?‚Äù Or ‚Äúi dont know‚Äù

Edit : they commented to reach out for any help
- and i reached out but no response. Sadly cant reach anyone. The hygiene is not maintained and all sanitisers and wet wipes are all empty always. Equipments are dirty and can see sweat marks everywhere.

author: Kelly Maloney
text: This is an incredible gym and location of Anytime Fitness. The equipment is clean, modern, the AC fresh, and employees excellent! The price was actually cheaper here than other locations and frankly for better overall quality! Also, the mall has refreshingly fun attractions and delicious food options to reward yourself after training =)

author: faith woo
text: This outlet would have to be my favourite gym in singapore currently. Been gym hopping every here and then, but i still keep coming back. the place is very clean, staff are friendly, equipment is well maintained, vibes are really pleasant, chargers are provided and the music is also very well chosen as well, and whenever people ask i will always recommend them to come here to get a good workout in!

author: Shihao Foo
text:
My favourite gym for a late night chill workout. The gym is relatively new and so the equipment and facilities are clean and fresh. The lighting isn‚Äôt too bright either. Overall the decor has the relaxing vibes of a bar.

+ve: training wise, it also has some less common machines that other AFs don‚Äôt have. For example, its assisted pullup machine is of the standing type (unlike the more common kneeling type). They also provide a helpful chart of their crowd levels at different times of the day (busiest between 7-9+pm on weekdays).

-ve: the biggest downside for me is that the gym has a no chalk policy, hence i only come for less intense workouts where i will not need chalk. Another point is that although the gym is well equipped, somehow I was not able to find a single abs crunch machine.

Finally as a more neutral point, for folks looking to train their glutes, i initially couldn‚Äôt find a booty builder machine here, but then I realised they have an equivalent called ‚Äúglute drive‚Äù. To me, the booty builder looks more aesthetic, but this equivalent looks functionally similar. Have not tried it though.

author: roche marion ella
text: My all time fave AF branch! Aside from near my workplace all staff are friendly and accommodating. Equipments are well maintained. Gym is spacious even jammed pack with yuppies. Plus star for the charger avail each corner of the gym. Simply the best!

author: Kid Carter Wagang
text:
Visited twice during my vacation in SG. I went at around 6/7am on Saturday and Monday. The place was relatively empty at that time except for a probably around 5/6 people. The place was big with an array of exercise equipment.

What amazed me was the abundance of sanitizer and towels, I think there is one for every machine. The shower area was also stocked with deodorant, for those just in case moments.

My mind was blown by the fact that they have supplement vendo machines.

Overall an upgrade from my AF home gym.

author: Natalie Ong
text: Genuinely convinced that csq‚Äôs af is one of the best if not the best in Singapore. It‚Äôs not the mere size but the equipments here are top-notch. Equipments aside, they have the friendliest team and great cleanliness! Albeit staying further away, it‚Äôs always worth the trip down. Nice to see that the traffic is picking up since their opening ‚Äî deserving of its popularity.

author: Subramanian PK
text:
I've been visiting few times this gym and I love this place given its very spacious, bright and cozy. Varieties of equipments helps the 'beginner' personnel like me.
I'll prefer this place even in the future also.

author: Nicholas Teo
text:
Customer service: 10/10
Gym cleanliness: 10/10

I really enjoyed my first time experience at AF! I was first greeted by staff member Daryl Lim and was arranged for an hour of free trial. I was keen to lose fat and gain muscle, but was completely new to the gym. Daryl was kind and helpful, he guided me around the gym and assisted me with some exercises that left me aching and sweating. Needless to say, it was a fulfilling experience, and I signed up for a membership on the spot.

I greatly recommend any gym-goer of any experience level to AFCSM!!

author: Dhaval Bhate
text:
Extremely disappointed with the experience at Anytime Fitness City Square Mall. I was overcharged on two separate occasions and despite having written confirmation from their own staff about billing adjustments, the team has refused to take responsibility or apologise.
They have been completely dismissive and unhelpful throughout the process. Instead of acknowledging their own mistake, they shifted the blame and brushed off all accountability once I transferred clubs. Even when presented with clear proof, they showed no willingness to resolve the issue or support a long-time member. This is not about the money. It is about how a business chooses to treat its members when things go wrong. The lack of basic professionalism, follow-through, and courtesy has been incredibly disappointing.
I would not recommend this location to anyone who values proper service and accountability.

author: Rachelle Ho
text: Anytime Fitness at City Square is clean, well-equipped, and convenient. The gym offers a wide range of machines and free weights, a spacious layout, and 24/7 secure access. Staff are friendly, helpful, and professional. The atmosphere is focused and supportive, with no crowding even during peak hours. Located in City Square Mall, it‚Äôs easy to access and perfect for anyone serious about staying fit.

author: Kimberly Wong
text: Clean. Well equipped. Spacious. May be crowded though during peak hours. It‚Äôs a popular gym. Good view.

author: Joanne Choo

author: Jasper Law

author: jia yang lee

author: faith woo

author: dillonbabb
text:
Decent gym, they‚Äôve packed in a lot of great equipment in the available space. Nice views and good music too. Could have better ventilation when it gets busy it gets quite musky. I think a better use of the staffs time would be cleaning and maintaining equipment. Trainers seem competent.

author: Sng Zach

author: David Goh

author: JoonBond

author: Alex Ng

author: Chiun Yi Yun

author: Roy Fong
text: Thank you to the staff and great location for AF, plenty of guided rails and free weight benches, treadmills, and a variety of machines.

author: zulaiha

author: Keven Chan
text: I‚Äôve been a member of Anytime Fitness at City Square Mall for a while now, and I have to say, the environment is fantastic! The staff, especially Dian and YY, are incredibly friendly, professional, and always willing to help. They create such a welcoming and motivating atmosphere that makes every visit enjoyable. author: Venkatesh Raj
text: Crowded like Taylor Swift concert, Most people park themselves in the equipment and sink in their phone. If you approach they get upset. Staff don't bother them to advise about gym best practices. If you want to use the phone why not do it sitting on a couch? Easily you end up wasting 30-40 mins in just waiting per visit to get a chance to use the equipments. Even treadmills are busy and there is just 1 cycle. Not just that, half of the cardio equipments are almost always under maintenance. Disappointing.

author: MrSavage Fox
text:
The Anytime Fitness at City Square Mall is one of the best new gyms in Singapore.

Gym Environment:
The gym is spacious and modern, with a clean and well-maintained atmosphere.

Equipment:
It boasts advanced equipment, including high-tech treadmills and exercise bikes, which really elevate the workout experience. The variety and quality of equipment are impressive, catering to all fitness needs.

Overall Experience:
This is definitely one of the top choices for anyone looking for a new gym in Singapore. With its large space, modern facilities, and top-of-the-line equipment, it stands out as one of the best Anytime Fitness locations around.

author: Michelle Teo
text: This outlet has a good range of machines, quite spacious and has a toilet within too (not all the outlets do). Pretty clean and there‚Äôs WiFi!

author: jiayang
text: ive been a member at Anytime Fitness for a while now, and I have to say, Yuyang is absolutely incredible! From the moment I walked in, Yuyang made me feel welcome and provided excellent guidance on using the equipment and structuring my workouts. They‚Äôre always positive, approachable, and ready to offer tips or advice whenever I need it. It‚Äôs clear that Yuyang truly cares about helping members reach their fitness goals. Their professionalism and upbeat attitude make every visit to the gym enjoyable. Highly recommend this location, and especially Yuyang, for anyone looking for great service and support on their fitness journey!

author: Syahirah MY
text: Came down to sign up with the gym and appreciate the service provided by the staff here. Received timely reply from them too on WhatsApp when I enquired about the promo.

author: myee choo

The staff is friendly and always ready to help, love that the gym is open 24/7, which is super convenient with my work schedule. Overall, it‚Äôs a clean, welcoming space that makes every workout enjoyable. Highly recommend for anyone looking for a reliable and flexible gym in the area!

author: Brian Chee
text: Donovan assisted with my enquiries and membership, and was very patient and helpful throughout the process! Appreciate the friendliness and kind assistance :)

author: Nam Seng Koh
text:
YY, very pleasant host.
Nice ambience but music a bit loud for senior. Not crowded before noon.

author: Cindy Kimberley (KC)
text: It was my first time at this AF today and I think this is gonna be my favourite! It's really clean and spacious. What I appreciated the most is that they have the cleaning agents at nearly all machines so it is so easy for me to clean down the machines without having to go around the whole  gym looking for the cleaning solution and rag. Going back again tomorrow!

author: Idrak Muttaqi
text: Very spacious and well equipped gym with friendly staff!

author: Siddharth Uthayasankar
text: The place is really nice and it's a good place to workout

author: Bab babs
text:
I‚Äôve been a member of this gym since it first opened, and honestly, it‚Äôs been getting worse over time. There are no wet wipes available, the towels are dirty and smelly, and most of the spray containers aren‚Äôt working properly or are empty. It‚Äôs unclear what the staff is doing,  it seems like they‚Äôre more focused on gathering 5-star reviews  rather than actually improving the gym‚Äôs facilities.

Reading all the glowing reviews here honestly feels misleading. There‚Äôs been no noticeable improvement since the gym opened. I really hope the staff and management are more transparent about the reviews. It feels like they‚Äôre deceiving people into thinking the gym is efficient and well-run, when in reality, the focus seems to be on collecting ratings rather than addressing the issues that matters!

The management should really take a closer look at the reviews here. and should improve the facility.

author: Jolene Chu

author: Elijah Dela Cruz

author: Muhammad Dhamiri

author: Waarith Zaman

author: yeow kiat Lau

author: Jiayee Ho
text: Been here for quite a while now, this is a spacious gym and equipments are really new and clean too.

author: Mohd Dzul

author: Almond

author: Vynsnt Ymmnwl
text:
Review: Inefficient Shower Allocation

The gym has a rather puzzling issue with the shower stall setup at this gym. Despite having more male members than female, and a consistent trend of more men being present at any time of the day, the shower facilities seem disproportionately allocated. Out of four stalls, two are reserved exclusively for women, while the remaining two are designated as unisex.

This arrangement leads to clear inefficiencies. The two female-exclusive stalls often appear underutilized, while the unisex stalls‚Äîused primarily by men due to their majority‚Äîtend to experience overcrowding and longer wait times. It feels like an unfair allocation of resources, where half of the facilities are reserved for a smaller demographic, leaving the majority to share the rest.

A more logical approach would be to allocate three stalls as unisex and one exclusively for females, or to adopt a dynamic system that adjusts based on demand during peak hours. It‚Äôs a shame, as the gym overall offers great amenities, but this lack of consideration for actual usage patterns detracts from the experience. A simple adjustment could make things much more equitable and efficient for everyone.

author: Ryan Chan
text:
Experienced a group of rude gym users demanding their use of equipment during peak hours and would have appreciated if staffs were more proactive on the ground, especially during peak hours, and recovery service after the incident was informed to one of the staff. This review is posted since I've yet to receive any updates from the staff after 5 days.

The incident happen on 30/4/24 between 7.25pm to 7.30pm at the caged rack located near to the Plated Leg Press. As the bench within the rack was empty with no sign of "booking" of the equipment such as placing of towel or phone on the bench, I went ahead to use it and completed 2 warm-up sets with no interference. 2 guys came to me after saying that they were using the bench. I politely told them that it was empty when I came to use and that there were no signs of anyone "booking" it and if they could use another empty bench that were located beside the Plated Chest Press machine. One of the guys rudely replied "No" and continued to give unreasonable reasoning as to how the bench was theirs. I did not want to cause a scene as I was clearly communicating with someone who isn't rationale and clearly egoistic. I offered to clean the equipment since I've used it but they rejected and laughed it off.

This incident was later communicated to a short Malay female staff and I requested her to investigate in this matter and get back to me regarding the resolution to such behavior within the facility and left my contact details with her. Given the benefit of doubt that the next day was Labour Day, I was expecting a response the day after. It has been 5 days since thus I decided to write this review with regards to both the standards of discipline within the gym as well as the proactiveness of the staff in this situation. I hope this group of individuals are not terrorizing other gym users with their unreasonable gym ethics else I would foresee more poor reviews in the future given the fact that this gym, in terms of equipment and staff politeness, are well above average.

For users who have seen this review and wonder if there's anything that can be done during such incident of unreasonable demands, I would highly suggest you to approach the gym staff immediately to sound it off.

author: Rainer Ong
text:
As a fitness enthusiast eager to maintain a healthy lifestyle, I recently decided to join Anytime Fitness at City Square Mall. Little did I know that this decision would not only positively impact my health but also provide me with exceptional service that exceeded all my expectations.

My journey with Anytime Fitness began with a warm welcome from the staff as soon as I entered the gym. Their friendly demeanor and willingness to assist made me feel right at home. The atmosphere was inviting, with state-of-the-art equipment neatly arranged, creating a motivating environment for a workout.

One aspect that truly stood out to me was the personalized attention I received from the trainers. Unlike other gyms where you are just another number, at Anytime Fitness, the trainers took the time to understand my fitness goals and tailored a workout plan specifically for me. Their expertise and constant encouragement not only pushed me to work harder but also helped me achieve results I had only dreamt of before.

Moreover, the cleanliness and maintenance of the facilities at City Square Mall were impeccable. The gym was spotless, equipment well-maintained, and hygiene standards were top-notch. This attention to detail not only reflected the professionalism of the staff but also ensured a comfortable and safe workout environment for all members.

Apart from the excellent facilities and training programs, another aspect that made my experience at Anytime Fitness unforgettable was the sense of community within the gym. I had the opportunity to participate in group fitness classes where I met like-minded individuals who shared the same passion for fitness. The camaraderie and support from fellow members created a positive and inclusive atmosphere that motivated me to push my limits and strive for my fitness goals.

In addition to the exceptional service and facilities, the convenience of having access to the gym 24/7 was a game-changer for me. Whether it was an early morning workout before work or a late-night session to de-stress, knowing that I could hit the gym anytime suited my busy schedule perfectly.

In conclusion, my experience at Anytime Fitness, City Square Mall, has been nothing short of phenomenal. The dedication of the staff, the high-quality facilities, the personalized training, and the sense of community have all played a significant role in not only transforming my fitness journey but also making it an enjoyable and rewarding experience. Anytime Fitness has truly set a benchmark in providing exemplary service, and I am grateful to be a part of such a remarkable fitness community.

text:
The best AF gym outlet I've ever been to! ü§©
- very spacious (despite having many equipment)
- stretching area has many accessories, floor is padded with soft mats (so no yoga mats)
- well lighted area throughout the gym (toilet facilities included)

- eg of equipment:
-- 4 power racks w/ island (ie 2 people can share this power rack, eg 1 squat + 1 DL)
-- 1 power rack (no island)
-- 2 Smith machines
-- 5 benches (adjustable)
-- 1 bench (fixed)
-- dumbbell rack up to 50 kg
(may get noisy during peak hours)

- built-in toilet facilities (uncommon for AF gym outlets)
-- 3 showers (1 designated for ladies)
-- 2 toilet cubicles (fancy looking + well ventilated, w/ well placed shelf + toilet roll + dustbin)
-- 1 changing room (1 full length mirror, 1 dustbin, 1 hanging rack, 1 small shelf)
-- small benches + shoe racks outside showers/toilet cubicles (thoughtful design!)

author: bot_59
text:
The resplendent realm of fitness at Anytime Fitness City Square Mall boasts an unparalleled symphony of modernity and function. Upon entering, one is ensconced in an ambience of sophistication, where the luminous sheen of polished machinery dances in harmony with the serenity of the surroundings.

The gym's pi√®ce de r√©sistance undoubtedly lies in its cavalcade of new-fangled machines. Each apparatus, an epitome of cutting-edge innovation, beckons with its beguiling allure and ergonomic design, promising an odyssey towards physical prowess. These marvels of engineering, bedecked in sleek contours and adorned with polished finishes, stand as veritable monuments to the fusion of aesthetics and utility.

Moreover, the gym's ambiance exudes an ineffable charm. The air, redolent with the invigorating scent of determination, resonates with the rhythmic symphony of clinking weights and the hushed determination of the earnest patrons. This amalgamation of vibrant energy and tranquil repose creates an oasis of motivation, where each visit becomes an exquisite sojourn towards personal zenith.

In sum, Anytime Fitness City Square Mall is an empyrean haven for fitness enthusiasts, a pantheon where the opulence of contemporary machinery meets the soothing embrace of an inviting atmosphere, ensuring an unparalleled journey towards fitness fruition.
